Definition.WordDefinition: Teenager \Teen"ag`er\ (t[=e]n"[=a]j`[~e]r), n. a person whose age is in the teens, i.e. one between the ages of 13 to 19 inclusive. [PJC]
teenager n : a juvenile between the onset of puberty and maturity [syn: {adolescent}, {stripling}]
